2 Security Management policy
QMSRS and its employees are jointly, individually and collectively responsible for maintaining a
secure workplace, and for the protection of QMSRS as well as client assets and information.
 QMSRS protects QMSRS employees, facilities and assets globally in the following
areas:
 Physical Security Systems
 Enterprise Access Control Security
 Systems and Monitoring
 Executive Support
 Crisis Management Coordination
 QMSRS monitors and reports QMSRS adherence to security and privacy policies and
control standards that comply with applicable key industry regulations, standards,
and best practices.
